result.title: ACM ICPC World Finals Warmup at Codemarshal on 7th May at 11 GMT
result.content: After a long break a World Finals Warmup (The UVa OJ series) with the join effort of DIU/Codemarshal/BAPS/UVa OJ. The Contest takes place at https://algo.codemarshal.org/contests . The contest will run for 12 hours for practice. An account must be created in codemarshal platform. The date and time can be found [here](http://www.timeanddate.com/worldclock/fixedtime.html?msg=ACM%20ICPC%20World%20Finals%20Warmup%20(Online%20Version)&iso=20160507T17&p1=73&ah=12)
